Welcome to BigPicture !

BigPicture is a notepad, in which you can pan and zoom 
infinitely many times. Just click anywhere and write !
You can now delete this text and start writing your own things !

* Pan : click and drag
* Zoom in : PageDown or CTRL+ or mousewheel or double-click 
* Zoom out : PageUp or CTRL- or mousewheel or CTRL+double-click
* Search : F3 or CTRL+F
* Move text : CTRL+click and drag
* See the big picture : F2
